| jstor=3182306}}</ref>、2001年[[中美撞机事件|中美撞机事件]]、2008年[[2008年西藏騷亂|西藏騷亂]]中西方媒體的偏見 <ref name="China Daily">{{cite news | title = Looking past Western media bias against China | url = http://www.china.org.cn/international/opinion/2008-02/28/content_11021569.htm | publisher = China Daily | date = 2008-02-28 | accessdate = 2009-06-07 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185409/http://www.china.org.cn/international/opinion/2008-02/28/content_11021569.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name ="China criticises">{{cite news | title = China criticises Western media | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7312376.stm | publisher = BBC News | date = 2008-03-25 | accessdate = 2009-06-07 | archive-date = 2008-03-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080331042128/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7312376.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>和[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會火炬接力|奧運會火炬接力]]境外群體示威抗議<ref name="erupt">{{cite news | title = Protests against ' Tibet independence' erupt in cities | url = http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2008-04/19/content_6629376.htm | publisher = China Daily | date = 2008-04-19 | accessdate = 2009-05-23 | archive-date = 2019-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191020201441/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2008-04/19/content_6629376.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>、而近年則主要圍繞著中西方的[[意識形態|意識形態]]衝突與西方國家對[[中华人民共和国人权|中华人民共和国人权]]上的争议等。

在21世紀初期，根據公共民意調查顯示，多數[[中國人|中國人]]曾經對[[美國|美國]]等西方國家持友好態度<ref name="hope and fear">{{cite web |title=Hope and Fear: Full report of C-100's Survey on American and Chinese Attitudes Toward Each Other |url=http://www.survey.committee100.org/2007/files/C100SurveyFullReport.pdf |publisher=Committee of 100 with assistance from Zogby International and Horizon Research Consultancy Group |year=2008 |accessdate=2009-06-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081109194104/http://www.survey.committee100.org/2007/files/C100SurveyFullReport.pdf |archivedate=2008-11-09 }}</ref>。但自[[中国共产党中央委员会总书记|中共中央总书记]][[习近平|习近平]]于2012年上台后，尤其是[[2018年中美贸易战|2018中美贸易战]]及[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]爆发之后，[[中國民族主義|中國民族主義]]被強化，在國内開展如[[四个自信|四个自信]]、[[中國夢|中國夢]]等[[中華人民共和國愛國主義教育|愛國主義教育活動]]鞏固統一意識形態 <ref name="Post-Communist Studies 1998. pp. 287-302">Zhao, Suisheng: "A State-led Nationalism: The Patriotic Education Campaign in Post-Tiananmen China", ''Communist and Post-Communist Studies'' , Vol. 31, No. 3. 1998. pp. 287-302</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/zh-hant/interactive/2018/11/25/world/asia/china-freedoms-control.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108121628/https://www.nytimes.com/zh-hant/interactive/2018/11/25/world/asia/china-freedoms-control.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在海外展開[[战狼外交|战狼外交]]，都在客觀上使中國人對西方國家的觀感急劇下降。現時，中國人普遍對西方保持負面觀感<ref>{{cite web |title=新加坡媒体：中国反制西方的底气来自哪里 |url=https://oversea.huanqiu.com/article/42WdsOeiVfq |website=环球时报 |accessdate=2021-04-16 |language=cn |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417150342/https://oversea.huanqiu.com/article/42WdsOeiVfq |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Welle (www.dw.com) |first1=Deutsche |title=中国反西方情绪令人担忧 {{!}} DW {{!}} 14.04.2008 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8D%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7/a-3265374 |website=DW.COM |accessdate=2021-04-16 |language=zh-CN |archive-date=2021-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526045428/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8D%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7/a-3265374 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，懷疑西方國家對中國的動機<ref name="hope and fear" />，其一般被認為源自百年來西方對中國欺侮的[[百年國恥|歷史記憶]]及当今西方政府的一些对华政策。 <ref name="chinese vent">{{cite news | title = Chinese vent anti-Western fury online | url = http://www.csmonitor.com/2008/0417/p01s01-woap.html | author = Peter Ford | publisher = The Christian Science Monitor | date = 2008-04-17 | accessdate = 2009-06-08 | archive-date = 2009-02-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090212143905/http://www.csmonitor.com/2008/0417/p01s01-woap.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

